sequenceDiagram
    participant App as 应用进程
    participant VRI as ViewRootImpl
    participant WMS as WMS (SystemServer)
    participant SF as SurfaceFlinger

    App->>VRI: WindowManager.addView(decorView, params)
    activate VRI
    VRI->>VRI: new ViewRootImpl()
    VRI->>VRI: setView(decorView, attrs)
    VRI->>VRI: requestLayout() [安排 performTraversals]

    VRI->>WMS: IWindowSession.addToDisplayAsUser()
    activate WMS
    WMS->>WMS: 权限检查 (系统窗口需 SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW)
    WMS->>WMS: Token 验证 (应用窗口需 ActivityRecord Token)
    WMS->>WMS: new WindowState
    WMS->>WMS: adjustWindowParamsLw() [策略调整]
    WMS->>WMS: createSurfaceControl()
    WMS->>WMS: openInputChannel() [输入事件通道]
    WMS->>WMS: assignWindowLayers() [Z-Order 排序]
    WMS-->>VRI: 返回 SurfaceControl + InputChannel
    deactivate WMS

    VRI->>VRI: performTraversals()
    VRI->>VRI: measure → layout → draw
    VRI->>SF: Surface.lockCanvas() / unlockCanvasAndPost()
    SF->>SF: 合成所有 Layer 并送显
    deactivate VRI
